name: Wukong Panda - KuD-054
description: He is a legendary mythical creature, born from a stone and have supernatural powers. He is so naughty, making mess everywhere he goes. He is like a disaster until heaven punish him to be imprisoned under a mountain. Hundred years pass by, one day a monk with his 2 disciples found him and freed him with conditions. He should become his disciple and come with him to get back the Sutras from the west. He agreed and join the monk, his character changes for the better and acquires many abilities along the way.
